node.text:
Today’s shoulder work 😏 this was a good one! 
I also did some core work and cardio! This is one of my favorite workouts I put together so far. I hope you enjoy 💛

Upright rows 10
Barbell press 10
X3

Standing or seated dumbbell press 10 
Arnold press 10
X3

Lateral raise ( not shown) 10
Seated single press 10
X3

Front raises (dumbbell or weight plate)  10
Dumbbell push press 10
X3
